title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: New friends or allies might be more influential than you realize at first glance. The Scorpio New Moon zaps your 11th House of Social Networks, infusing your life with possibilities for significant transformation. But you may not fully grasp how potent these opportunities could be now because true power doesnt need to be flashy. Your access to external authority is likely growing because youre coming to trust your own internal authority and autonomy. Entrepreneur Payal Kadakia wrote, Surround yourself with people who only lift you higher. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
